Package: SpeClust
Type: Package
Title: Functions useful for spectral clustering project
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-04-23
Author: Yilin Zhang <yzhang672@wisc.edu>
Maintainer: Yilin Zhang <yzhang672@wisc.edu>
Description: This package contains functions to create adjacency matrix, 
             combine sparse matrices, do SVD sorted by time, clean text,
             find frequency of words, draw balloonPlot, etc. Those functions
             are useful for spectral clustering project.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
License: MIT
LazyData: true
Imports:
    dplyr,
    irlba,
    RSQLite,
    Matrix
Suggests:
    knitr,
    devtools,
    roxygen2,
    testthat
